{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881169269,"sessionID":"ses_2853c090cffeel1fslks36nfqD","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac41c61001kcpE2249iKFJu7","messageID":"msg_d7ac40a700012vhAq8jlpW7ETg","sessionID":"ses_2853c090cffeel1fslks36nfqD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_0f4c8b8f0d7d4d7eb8f7da04","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 RBAC 配置，将 ServiceAccount、Role/ClusterRole、RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding 从 Helm Chart 模板中独立出来，形成可单独部署的 RBAC 配置模块。该 RBAC 配置是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的权限管理基础，支撑 Workload Manager 和 Router 的访问控制需求。\n6: \n7: 目标是：\n8: \n9: 1. **权限最小化** - 为每个组件分配精确的 RBAC 权限，遵循 least privilege 原则\n10: 2. **模块化部署** - RBAC 配置可独立于 Helm Chart 单独部署，支持预创建权限\n11: 3. **多租户支持** - 通过 Role/RoleBinding 支持 namespace-scoped 权限，实现多租户隔离\n12: 4. **审计友好** - 独立的 RBAC 配置便于权限审计和安全审查\n13: 5. **环境兼容性** - 支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化权限配置\n14: \n15: 本实现基于 manifests/design.md 和 manifests/delta-spec.md 的规范，遵循 Kubernetes RBAC 最佳实践。\n16: \n17: ## Scope\n18: \n19: **Module:** manifests  \n20: **Language:** YAML  \n21: **Size:** M\n22: \n23: 本 AR 包含：\n24: \n25: - **包含内容：**\n26:   - Workload Manager ServiceAccount 定义\n27:   - Workload Manager ClusterRole 定义（cluster-wide 权限）\n28:   - Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding 定义\n29:   - Router ServiceAccount 定义（可选）\n30:   - Router Role 定义（namespace-scoped 权限，可选）\n31:   - Router RoleBinding 定义（可选）\n32:   - RBAC 配置验证脚本\n33:   - 使用文档和权限说明\n34: \n35: - **不包含内容：**\n36:   - Helm Chart 模板（由 AR-030 管理）\n37:   - Kubernetes 集群配置\n38:   - 应用层代码修改\n39:   - 认证/授权逻辑实现\n40: \n41: ## Current State Analysis\n42: \n43: ### 现有 RBAC 配置\n44: \n45: 根据 `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`：\n46: - Workload Manager ServiceAccount 已定义\n47: - Workload Manager ClusterRole 已定义，包含完整的 CRD、Pods、Secrets 权限\n48: - Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding 已定义\n49: \n50: 根据 `manifests/design.md`：\n51: - Router RBAC 设计为可选的 namespace-scoped Role + RoleBinding\n52: - Router 默认不创建 RBAC，通过 `router.rbac.create` 控制\n53: \n54: ### 参考设计规范\n55: \n56: 根据 `manifests/delta-spec.md` REQ-030.5 和 REQ-030.6：\n57: \n58: **Workload Manager RBAC 要求：**\n59: - ServiceAccount: `workloadmanager`，位于 release namespace\n60: - ClusterRole: `workloadmanager`，包含以下权限：\n61:   - `agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxes`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n62:   - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxclaims`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n63:   - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxtemplates`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n64:   - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n65:   - `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/sandboxwarmpools/status`: get, update, patch\n66:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n67:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/status`: get, update, patch\n68:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/codeinterpreters/finalizers`: update\n69:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes`: get, list, watch\n70:   - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/agentruntimes/status`: update, patch\n71:   - `pods`: get, list, watch\n72:   - `authentication.k8s.io/tokenreviews`: create\n73:   - `secrets`: get, list, watch, create, update, patch, delete\n74: - ClusterRoleBinding: 绑定 ServiceAccount 到 ClusterRole\n75: \n76: **Router RBAC 要求：**\n77: - ServiceAccount: `agentcube-router`（或从 values 配置）\n78: - Role: namespace-scoped，包含 secrets 权限\n79: - RoleBinding: 绑定 ServiceAccount 到 Role\n80: - 可选：通过 `router.rbac.create` 控制是否创建\n81: \n82: ### 差距分析\n83: \n84: 1. **缺少独立 RBAC 配置** - 当前 RBAC 嵌入在 Helm Chart 中，无法单独部署\n85: 2. **缺少权限说明文档** - 未明确说明每个权限的用途和必要性\n86: 3. **缺少审计支持** - 无权限审计工具或检查清单\n87: 4. **多租户支持不完整** - 缺少针对多租户场景的 Role/RoleBinding 配置\n88: \n89: ### manifests/design.md 关键要求\n90: \n91: 1. **权限最小化** - RBAC 权限应精确到每个资源操作\n92: 2. **命名空间隔离** - Router RBAC 应为 namespace-scoped\n93: 3. **可选组件支持** - Router RBAC 默认禁用，按需启用\n94: 4. **可审计性** - RBAC 配置应易于审查和验证\n95: \n96: ## Proposed Changes\n97: \n98: ### 1. 目录结构\n99: \n100: ```\n101: manifests/rbac/\n102: ├── README.md                       # RBAC 配置说明\n103: ├── workloadmanager/\n104: │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Workload Manager ServiceAccount\n105: │   ├── clusterrole.yaml            # Workload Manager ClusterRole\n106: │   └── clusterrolebinding.yaml     # Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding\n107: ├── router/\n108: │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # Router ServiceAccount (可选)\n109: │   ├── role.yaml                   # Router Role (可选)\n110: │   └── rolebinding.yaml            # Router RoleBinding (可选)\n111: ├── kustomization.yaml              # Kustomize 配置\n112: └── validate.sh                     # RBAC 验证脚本\n113: ```\n114: \n115: ### 2. Workload Manager ServiceAccount\n116: \n117: ```yaml\n118: # manifests/rbac/workloadmanager/serviceaccount.yaml\n119: apiVersion: v1\n120: kind: ServiceAccount\n121: metadata:\n122:   name: workloadmanager\n123:   namespace: agentcube-system\n124:   labels:\n125:     app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n126:     app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n127: ---\n128: ```\n129: \n130: ### 3. Workload Manager ClusterRole\n131: \n132: ```yaml\n133: # manifests/rbac/workloadmanager/clusterrole.yaml\n134: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n135: kind: ClusterRole\n136: metadata:\n137:   name: workloadmanager\n138:   labels:\n139:     app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n140:     app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n141: rules:\n142:   # Agent Sandbox resources\n143:   - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n144:     resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n145:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n146:   \n147:   # Agent Extension resources\n148:   - apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n149:     resources: [\"sandboxclaims\", \"sandboxtemplates\", \"sandboxwarmpools\"]\n150:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n151:   \n152:   # Warm pool status subresource\n153:   - apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n154:     resources: [\"sandboxwarmpools/status\"]\n155:     verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n156:   \n157:   # CodeInterpreter runtime resources\n158:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n159:     resources: [\"codeinterpreters\"]\n160:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n161:   \n162:   # CodeInterpreter status subresource\n163:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n164:     resources: [\"codeinterpreters/status\"]\n165:     verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n166:   \n167:   # CodeInterpreter finalizers\n168:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n169:     resources: [\"codeinterpreters/finalizers\"]\n170:     verbs: [\"update\"]\n171:   \n172:   # AgentRuntime resources (read-only)\n173:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n174:     resources: [\"agentruntimes\"]\n175:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n176:   \n177:   # AgentRuntime status subresource\n178:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n179:     resources: [\"agentruntimes/status\"]\n180:     verbs: [\"update\", \"patch\"]\n181:   \n182:   # Pod resources (read-only for status)\n183:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n184:     resources: [\"pods\"]\n185:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n186:   \n187:   # Token review for authentication\n188:   - apiGroups: [\"authentication.k8s.io\"]\n189:     resources: [\"tokenreviews\"]\n190:     verbs: [\"create\"]\n191:   \n192:   # Secrets for credentials and configs\n193:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n194:     resources: [\"secrets\"]\n195:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n196: ```\n197: \n198: ### 4. Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding\n199: \n200: ```yaml\n201: # manifests/rbac/workloadmanager/clusterrolebinding.yaml\n202: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n203: kind: ClusterRoleBinding\n204: metadata:\n205:   name: workloadmanager\n206:   labels:\n207:     app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n208:     app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n209: subjects:\n210:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n211:     name: workloadmanager\n212:     namespace: agentcube-system\n213: roleRef:\n214:   kind: ClusterRole\n215:   name: workloadmanager\n216:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n217: ```\n218: \n219: ### 5. Router ServiceAccount (Optional)\n220: \n221: ```yaml\n222: # manifests/rbac/router/serviceaccount.yaml\n223: apiVersion: v1\n224: kind: ServiceAccount\n225: metadata:\n226:   name: agentcube-router\n227:   namespace: agentcube-system\n228:   labels:\n229:     app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n230:     app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n231:   annotations:\n232:     description: \"Optional - only required when router.rbac.create=true\"\n233: ---\n234: ```\n235: \n236: ### 6. Router Role (Optional)\n237: \n238: ```yaml\n239: # manifests/rbac/router/role.yaml\n240: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n241: kind: Role\n242: metadata:\n243:   name: agentcube-router\n244:   namespace: agentcube-system\n245:   labels:\n246:     app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n247:     app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n248:   annotations:\n249:     description: \"Optional - namespace-scoped RBAC for Router\"\n250: rules:\n251:   # Secrets for session tokens and credentials\n252:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n253:     resources: [\"secrets\"]\n254:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n255: ```\n256: \n257: ### 7. Router RoleBinding (Optional)\n258: \n259: ```yaml\n260: # manifests/rbac/router/rolebinding.yaml\n261: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n262: kind: RoleBinding\n263: metadata:\n264:   name: agentcube-router\n265:   namespace: agentcube-system\n266:   labels:\n267:     app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n268:     app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n269: subjects:\n270:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n271:     name: agentcube-router\n272:     namespace: agentcube-system\n273: roleRef:\n274:   kind: Role\n275:   name: agentcube-router\n276:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n277: ```\n278: \n279: ### 8. Kustomize Configuration\n280: \n281: ```yaml\n282: # manifests/rbac/kustomization.yaml\n283: apiVersion: kustomize.config.k8s.io/v1beta1\n284: kind: Kustomization\n285: \n286: namespace: agentcube-system\n287: \n288: resources:\n289:   - workloadmanager/serviceaccount.yaml\n290:   - workloadmanager/clusterrole.yaml\n291:   - workloadmanager/clusterrolebinding.yaml\n292:   # Optional Router RBAC - uncomment to enable\n293:   # - router/serviceaccount.yaml\n294:   # - router/role.yaml\n295:   # - router/rolebinding.yaml\n296: \n297: commonLabels:\n298:   app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube\n299:   app.kubernetes.io/component: rbac\n300: ```\n301: \n302: ### 9. RBAC 验证脚本\n303: \n304: ```bash\n305: #!/bin/bash\n306: # manifests/rbac/validate.sh\n307: \n308: set -e\n309: \n310: NAMESPACE=\"${NAMESPACE:-agentcube-system}\"\n311: \n312: echo \"Validating RBAC configuration...\"\n313: \n314: # Check Workload Manager ServiceAccount\n315: if kubectl get serviceaccount workloadmanager -n \"$NAMESPACE\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n316:   echo \"✓ Workload Manager ServiceAccount exists\"\n317: else\n318:   echo \"✗ Workload Manager ServiceAccount missing\"\n319:   exit 1\n320: fi\n321: \n322: # Check Workload Manager ClusterRole\n323: if kubectl get clusterrole workloadmanager > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n324:   echo \"✓ Workload Manager ClusterRole exists\"\n325: else\n326:   echo \"✗ Workload Manager ClusterRole missing\"\n327:   exit 1\n328: fi\n329: \n330: # Check Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding\n331: if kubectl get clusterrolebinding workloadmanager > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n332:   echo \"✓ Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding exists\"\n333: else\n334:   echo \"✗ Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding missing\"\n335:   exit 1\n336: fi\n337: \n338: # Verify ClusterRole permissions\n339: echo \"\"\n340: echo \"Verifying ClusterRole permissions...\"\n341: PERMISSIONS=$(kubectl get clusterrole workloadmanager -o jsonpath='{.rules[*].apiGroups[*]}')\n342: if echo \"$PERMISSIONS\" | grep -q \"agents.x-k8s.io\"; then\n343:   echo \"✓ agents.x-k8s.io API group present\"\n344: else\n345:   echo \"✗ agents.x-k8s.io API group missing\"\n346:   exit 1\n347: fi\n348: \n349: if echo \"$PERMISSIONS\" | grep -q \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"; then\n350:   echo \"✓ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh API group present\"\n351: else\n352:   echo \"✗ runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh API group missing\"\n353:   exit 1\n354: fi\n355: \n356: echo \"\"\n357: echo \"RBAC validation passed!\"\n358: ```\n359: \n360: ## Impact Analysis\n361: \n362: ### 依赖影响\n363: \n364: | 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n365: |--------|------|------|\n366: | Kubernetes | ≥1.21 | RBAC API |\n367: | kubectl | ≥1.21 | 部署和验证 |\n368: | Kustomize | ≥4.0 | 配置管理 |\n369: \n370: ### 模块依赖关系\n371: \n372: ```\n373: manifests/rbac/\n374: ├── workloadmanager/\n375: │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # 无依赖\n376: │   ├── clusterrole.yaml            # 依赖 CRD 定义 (AR-017)\n377: │   └── clusterrolebinding.yaml     # 依赖 ServiceAccount + ClusterRole\n378: ├── router/\n379: │   ├── serviceaccount.yaml         # 无依赖\n380: │   ├── role.yaml                   # 无依赖\n381: │   └── rolebinding.yaml            # 依赖 ServiceAccount + Role\n382: ├── kustomization.yaml              # 依赖所有 RBAC 文件\n383: └── validate.sh                     # 依赖 kubectl\n384: ```\n385: \n386: ### 向后兼容性\n387: \n388: - 首次实现，无破坏性变更风险\n389: - 与 AR-030 Helm Chart 中的 RBAC 配置兼容（内容一致，组织形式不同）\n390: - 支持独立部署或与 Helm Chart 协同部署\n391: \n392: ### 测试影响\n393: \n394: - 需要验证 RBAC 权限的正确性（`kubectl auth can-i`）\n395: - 需要验证命名空间隔离（Router Role 应为 namespace-scoped）\n396: - 需要验证 ServiceAccount 与 Role/ClusterRole 的绑定关系\n397: \n398: ### 与 AR-030 的关系\n399: \n400: AR-030 的 Helm Chart 中包含的 RBAC 模板与本 AR 的独立 RBAC 配置内容一致，但使用场景不同：\n401: \n402: | 场景 | AR-030 (Helm) | AR-031 (独立) |\n403: |------|---------------|---------------|\n404: | 快速部署 | ✓ | ✗ |\n405: | 预创建权限 | ✗ | ✓ |\n406: | 权限审计 | ✗ | ✓ |\n407: | 多租户配置 | ✗ | ✓ |\n408: | 环境隔离 | 通过 values | 通过 kustomize |\n409: \n410: 推荐流程：先使用 AR-031 预创建 RBAC，再使用 AR-030 Helm Chart 部署应用。\n411: \n412: ## Alternatives Considered\n413: \n414: ### 方案 1: 仅使用 Helm Chart RBAC（不独立）\n415: \n416: **优点:**\n417: - 简单，单一部署单元\n418: - 无需额外工具\n419: \n420: **缺点:**\n421: - 无法预创建权限\n422: - 权限审计困难\n423: - 与 Helm release 绑定，难以跨环境复用\n424: \n425: **决策:** 提供独立 RBAC 配置，支持与 Helm 解耦部署。\n426: \n427: ### 方案 2: 使用 RBAC Management Operator\n428: \n429: **优点:**\n430: - 自动化 RBAC 生命周期管理\n431: - 支持动态权限调整\n432: \n433: **缺点:**\n434: - 增加运维复杂度\n435: - 需要额外的 Operator 部署\n436: \n437: **决策:** 采用静态 YAML 配置，保持简单可控。\n438: \n439: ### 方案 3: 单一巨型 RBAC 文件\n440: \n441: **优点:**\n442: - 文件数量少\n443: - 易于复制\n444: \n445: **缺点:**\n446: - 难以维护\n447: - 不支持按需启用组件\n448: \n449: **决策:** 采用模块化组织（每个组件独立目录），提高可维护性。\n450: \n451: ### 方案 4: ClusterRole vs Role 选择\n452: \n453: **Workload Manager:** 选择 ClusterRole，因为需要：\n454: - 访问跨 namespace 的 CRD\n455: - 管理多个租户的 Sandbox\n456: \n457: **Router:** 选择 Role，因为：\n458: - 仅需访问本 namespace 的 Secrets\n459: - 支持多租户隔离\n460: \n461: **决策:** 根据组件需求选择合适的 RBAC 作用域。\n462: \n463: ## Testing Strategy\n464: \n465: ### 权限验证\n466: \n467: 1. **Workload Manager 权限验证**\n468:    ```bash\n469:    kubectl auth can-i create sandboxes --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube-system:workloadmanager\n470:    kubectl auth can-i get codeinterpreters --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube-system:workloadmanager\n471:    kubectl auth can-i update secrets --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube-system:workloadmanager\n472:    ```\n473: \n474: 2. **Router 权限验证**\n475:    ```bash\n476:    kubectl auth can-i get secrets -n agentcube-system --as=system:serviceaccount:agentcube-system:agentcube-router\n477:    ```\n478: \n479: ### 隔离验证\n480: \n481: 1. **命名空间隔离** - 验证 Router Role 无法访问其他 namespace\n482: 2. **权限最小化** - 验证 RBAC 仅包含必需权限\n483: \n484: ### 集成测试\n485: \n486: 1. **Kind 集群测试** - 在 Kind 集群上实际安装验证\n487: 2. **应用联调** - 验证 Workload Manager 和 Router 能正常使用分配的权限\n488: \n489: ### 测试覆盖目标\n490: \n491: - ServiceAccount: 100%（所有组件）\n492: - ClusterRole/Role: 100%（所有权限规则）\n493: - Binding: 100%（所有绑定关系）\n494: - 验证脚本: 100%（所有检查项）\n495: \n496: ## Acceptance Criteria\n497: \n498: - [ ] Workload Manager ServiceAccount 可创建\n499: - [ ] Workload Manager ClusterRole 权限完整\n500: - [ ] Workload Manager ClusterRoleBinding 正确绑定\n501: - [ ] Router ServiceAccount 可创建（可选）\n502: - [ ] Router Role 权限正确（可选）\n503: - [ ] Router RoleBinding 正确绑定（可选）\n504: - [ ] `kubectl apply -k` 成功\n505: - [ ] 验证脚本通过所有检查\n506: - [ ] 权限验证通过（`kubectl auth can-i`）\n507: - [ ] 文档完整（权限说明、使用示例）\n508: \n509: ## Dependencies\n510: \n511: ### 必需依赖\n512: - Kubernetes ≥1.21（RBAC API）\n513: - kubectl ≥1.21\n514: - Kustomize ≥4.0\n515: \n516: ### 被依赖\n517: - AR-017 (CRD 定义) - ClusterRole 权限依赖 CRD\n518: - AR-030 (Helm Chart) - 可选协同部署\n519: \n520: ## Migration Notes\n521: \n522: ### 从 Helm Chart RBAC 迁移\n523: \n524: 1. 备份现有 RBAC 配置\n525:    ```bash\n526:    kubectl get serviceaccount,clusterrole,clusterrolebinding -l app.kubernetes.io/name=workloadmanager -o yaml > backup.yaml\n527:    ```\n528: \n529: 2. 应用独立 RBAC 配置\n530:    ```bash\n531:    kubectl apply -k manifests/rbac/\n532:    ```\n533: \n534: 3. 验证权限\n535:    ```bash\n536:    ./manifests/rbac/validate.sh\n537:    ```\n538: \n539: 4. 更新 Helm Chart（可选）\n540:    - 禁用 Helm Chart 中的 RBAC 创建\n541:    - 或保留 Helm Chart RBAC（内容一致，无冲突）\n542: \n543: ### 破坏性变更\n544: 无 - 首次实现。\n545: \n546: ### 行为变更\n547: - RBAC 配置从 Helm Chart 中解耦\n548: - 支持独立部署和版本控制\n549: \n550: ## Open Questions\n551: \n552: 1. 是否需要支持自定义命名空间？（通过 kustomize namespace 字段）\n553: 2. 是否需要提供 RBAC 审计日志？（待需求明确）\n554: 3. 是否需要支持动态权限更新？（待需求明确）\n555: \n556: ## References\n557: \n558: - `manifests/design.md` - Manifests 设计文档\n559: - `manifests/delta-spec.md` - Manifests 规范（REQ-030.5, REQ-030.6）\n560: - `manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` - 现有 Helm RBAC 模板\n561: - Kubernetes RBAC Best Practices: https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/access-authn-authz/rbac/\n562: - Kustomize Documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/manage-kubernetes-objects/kustomization/\n\n(End of file - total 562 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-031: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 RBAC 配置，将 ServiceAccount、Role/ClusterRole、RoleBinding/ClusterRoleBinding 从 Helm Chart 模板中独立出来，形成可单独部署的 RBAC 配置模块。该 RBAC 配置是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的权限管理基础，支撑 Workload Manager 和 Router 的访问控制需求。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **权限最小化** - 为每个组件分配精确的 RBAC 权限，遵循 least privilege 原则\n2. **模块化部署** - RBAC 配置可独立于 Helm Chart 单独部署，支持预创建权限\n3. **多租户支持** - 通过 Role/RoleBinding 支持 namespace-scoped 权限，实现多租户隔离\n4. **审计友好** - 独立的 RBAC 配置便于权限审计和安全审查\n5. **环境兼容性** - 支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化权限配置\n\n本实现基于 manifests/design.md 和 manifests/delta-spec.md 的规范，遵循 Kubernetes RBAC 最佳实践。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** manifests  \n**Language:** YAML  ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-031/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775881169237,"end":1775881169267}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881169273,"sessionID":"ses_2853c090cffeel1fslks36nfqD","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac42200001NPeZvwQdKzJghN","messageID":"msg_d7ac40a700012vhAq8jlpW7ETg","sessionID":"ses_2853c090cffeel1fslks36nfqD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_bed411c64d004fccace9f816","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Helm Chart 模板与 Values 配置，提供标准的 Kubernetes 部署能力。该 Helm Chart 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的核心部署载体，支撑 Workload Manager、Router、以及可选的 Volcano Agent Scheduler 的安装与管理。\n6: \n7: 目标是：\n8: \n9: 1. **标准化部署流程** - 通过 Helm Chart 统一控制平面组件的部署配置，支持一键安装/升级\n10: 2. **配置灵活性** - 通过 values.yaml 提供完整的配置项，支持镜像、资源、副本数等自定义\n11: 3. **CRD 生命周期管理** - 将 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 纳入 Chart 管理，随 Chart 安装\n12: 4. **Redis 连接配置** - 支持 Redis 地址和认证的灵活配置，满足 Workload Manager 和 Router 运行时需求\n13: 5. **可选组件支持** - 支持 Router RBAC、Volcano Scheduler 等可选组件的按需启用\n14: 6. **多环境兼容** - 通过 values 覆盖支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化配置\n15: \n16: 本实现基于 deployment/spec.md 和 deployment/design.md 的规范，遵循 Helm 3 最佳实践。\n17: \n18: ## Scope\n19: \n20: **Module:** manifests  \n21: **Language:** YAML  \n22: **Size:** L\n23: \n24: 本 AR 包含：\n25: \n26: - **包含内容：**\n27:   - Chart.yaml 实现（apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0）\n28:   - values.yaml 完整配置树（Redis、Router、WorkloadManager、Volcano Scheduler）\n29:   - Workload Manager Deployment 和 Service 模板\n30:   - Router Deployment 和 Service 模板\n31:   - Workload Manager RBAC 资源（ServiceAccount、ClusterRole、ClusterRoleBinding）\n32:   - Router 可选 RBAC 资源（ServiceAccount、Role、RoleBinding）\n33:   - Volcano Agent Scheduler 可选资源（ServiceAccount、ConfigMap、ClusterRole、ClusterRoleBinding、Service、Deployment）\n34:   - CRD 文件（agentruntimes、codeinterpreters）\n35:   - .helmignore 文件\n36:   - 单元测试（values 验证、模板渲染测试）\n37:   - 安装文档和使用示例\n38: \n39: - **不包含内容：**\n40:   - Docker 镜像构建（由 docker/Dockerfile 单独管理）\n41:   - Redis 集群部署（作为外部依赖）\n42:   - 应用层代码修改\n43:   - 客户端 SDK 或 CLI 工具\n44: \n45: ## Current State Analysis\n46: \n47: ### 现有 manifests 结构\n48: \n49: 根据 `manifests/charts/base/` 目录：\n50: - `crds/agentruntime.yaml` 已存在，包含 AgentRuntime CRD 定义\n51: - 缺少 CodeInterpreter CRD\n52: - 缺少 Chart.yaml、values.yaml 和 templates/\n53: \n54: ### 参考设计规范\n55: \n56: 根据 `deployment/design.md` 和 `deployment/spec.md`：\n57: \n58: **Chart.yaml 要求：**\n59: - apiVersion: v1\n60: - name: agentcube\n61: - version: 0.1.0\n62: - appVersion: 1.0.0\n63: \n64: **values.yaml 关键配置树：**\n65: - redis.addr / redis.password（必需配置）\n66: - router.replicas/image/service/resources/config/extraEnv/serviceAccountName/rbac\n67: - workloadmanager.replicas/image/service/resources/extraEnv\n68: - volcano.scheduler.enabled 及相关配置\n69: \n70: **模板文件要求：**\n71: - `templates/workloadmanager.yaml`: Deployment + Service\n72: - `templates/agentcube-router.yaml`: Deployment + Service\n73: - `templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`: ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\n74: - `templates/rbac-router.yaml`: 可选的 Router RBAC\n75: - `templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml`: 可选的 Volcano Scheduler\n76: \n77: **CRD 要求：**\n78: - `crds/agentruntimes`: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n79: - `crds/codeinterpreters`: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n80: \n81: ### 差距分析\n82: \n83: 1. **Chart 结构不完整** - 仅有 CRD，缺少 Chart.yaml、values.yaml 和 templates\n84: 2. **CRD 不完整** - 缺少 CodeInterpreter CRD\n85: 3. **缺少环境配置支持** - 无 values 覆盖机制，无法支持多环境部署\n86: 4. **缺少 RBAC 定义** - Workload Manager 和 Router 的 RBAC 资源未定义\n87: 5. **缺少可选组件支持** - Volcano Scheduler 等可选组件无法按需启用\n88: \n89: ### deployment/spec.md 关键要求\n90: \n91: 1. **Redis 配置** - `redis.addr` 和 `redis.password` 必须通过 values 配置，注入到 Pod 环境变量\n92: 2. **Workload Manager 形状** - Deployment + Service，支持 replicas、image、resources、health probes\n93: 3. **Router 形状** - Deployment + Service，支持 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 动态构建\n94: 4. **RBAC 权限** - Workload Manager 需要 ClusterRole 访问 CRD、Pods、Secrets 等\n95: 5. **可选 Router RBAC** - `router.rbac.create` 控制是否创建 namespace-scoped RBAC\n96: 6. **可选 Volcano Scheduler** - `volcano.scheduler.enabled` 控制是否部署\n97: \n98: ## Proposed Changes\n99: \n100: ### 1. Chart.yaml\n101: \n102: ```yaml\n103: # manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml\n104: apiVersion: v1\n105: name: agentcube\n106: description: A Helm chart for AgentCube\n107: version: 0.1.0\n108: appVersion: \"1.0.0\"\n109: keywords:\n110:   - agent\n111:   - sandbox\n112:   - kubernetes\n113:   - volcano\n114: home: https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n115: sources:\n116:   - https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n117: maintainers:\n118:   - name: Volcano Authors\n119:     email: volcano-sh@googlegroups.com\n120: ```\n121: \n122: ### 2. values.yaml\n123: \n124: ```yaml\n125: # manifests/charts/base/values.yaml\n126: # Default values for AgentCube.\n127: \n128: # Image pull secrets for all components\n129: imagePullSecrets: []\n130: \n131: # Override chart names\n132: nameOverride: \"\"\n133: fullnameOverride: \"\"\n134: \n135: # Redis configuration (required)\n136: # Redis address and password for Workload Manager and Router connectivity\n137: redis:\n138:   addr: \"\"          # e.g., \"redis.redis-system.svc.cluster.local:6379\"\n139:   password: \"\"      # Empty if Redis has no authentication\n140: \n141: # Router configuration\n142: router:\n143:   replicas: 1\n144:   image:\n145:     repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router\n146:     pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n147:     tag: \"latest\"\n148:   service:\n149:     type: ClusterIP\n150:     port: 8080\n151:     targetPort: 8080\n152:   resources:\n153:     limits:\n154:       cpu: 500m\n155:       memory: 512Mi\n156:     requests:\n157:       cpu: 100m\n158:       memory: 128Mi\n159:   # Additional container configuration\n160:   config: {}\n161:   extraEnv: []\n162:   serviceAccountName: \"\"  # Empty means auto-generated or default\n163:   rbac:\n164:     create: false  # Enable namespace-scoped RBAC for Router\n165: \n166: # Workload Manager configuration\n167: workloadmanager:\n168:   replicas: 1\n169:   image:\n170:     repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager\n171:     pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n172:     tag: \"latest\"\n173:   service:\n174:     type: ClusterIP\n175:     port: 8080\n176:   resources:\n177:     limits:\n178:       cpu: 500m\n179:       memory: 512Mi\n180:     requests:\n181:       cpu: 100m\n182:       memory: 128Mi\n183:   extraEnv: []\n184: \n185: # Volcano Agent Scheduler (optional)\n186: volcano:\n187:   scheduler:\n188:     enabled: false\n189:     replicas: 1\n190:     image:\n191:       repository: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler\n192:       pullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n193:       tag: \"latest\"\n194: ```\n195: \n196: ### 3. Workload Manager Template\n197: \n198: ```yaml\n199: # manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml\n200: apiVersion: apps/v1\n201: kind: Deployment\n202: metadata:\n203:   name: workloadmanager\n204:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n205:   labels:\n206:     app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n207:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n208: spec:\n209:   replicas: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.replicas }}\n210:   selector:\n211:     matchLabels:\n212:       app: workloadmanager\n213:   template:\n214:     metadata:\n215:       labels:\n216:         app: workloadmanager\n217:     spec:\n218:       {{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\n219:       imagePullSecrets:\n220:         {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n221:       {{- end }}\n222:       serviceAccountName: workloadmanager\n223:       containers:\n224:         - name: workloadmanager\n225:           image: \"{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.tag }}\"\n226:           imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.image.pullPolicy }}\n227:           ports:\n228:             - name: http\n229:               containerPort: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n230:               protocol: TCP\n231:           env:\n232:             - name: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\n233:               valueFrom:\n234:                 fieldRef:\n235:                   fieldPath: metadata.namespace\n236:             - name: REDIS_ADDR\n237:               value: {{ .Values.redis.addr | quote }}\n238:             - name: REDIS_PASSWORD\n239:               valueFrom:\n240:                 secretKeyRef:\n241:                   name: {{ .Release.Name }}-redis\n242:                   key: password\n243:                   optional: true\n244:             {{- with .Values.workloadmanager.extraEnv }}\n245:             {{- toYaml . | nindent 12 }}\n246:             {{- end }}\n247:           args:\n248:             - --port={{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n249:             - --runtime-class-name=\n250:           resources:\n251:             {{- toYaml .Values.workloadmanager.resources | nindent 12 }}\n252:           livenessProbe:\n253:             httpGet:\n254:               path: /health\n255:               port: http\n256:             initialDelaySeconds: 10\n257:             periodSeconds: 10\n258:           readinessProbe:\n259:             httpGet:\n260:               path: /health\n261:               port: http\n262:             initialDelaySeconds: 5\n263:             periodSeconds: 5\n264: ---\n265: apiVersion: v1\n266: kind: Service\n267: metadata:\n268:   name: workloadmanager\n269:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n270:   labels:\n271:     app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n272:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n273: spec:\n274:   type: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.type }}\n275:   ports:\n276:     - port: {{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\n277:       targetPort: http\n278:       protocol: TCP\n279:       name: http\n280:   selector:\n281:     app: workloadmanager\n282: ```\n283: \n284: ### 4. Router Template\n285: \n286: ```yaml\n287: # manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml\n288: apiVersion: apps/v1\n289: kind: Deployment\n290: metadata:\n291:   name: agentcube-router\n292:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n293:   labels:\n294:     app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n295:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n296: spec:\n297:   replicas: {{ .Values.router.replicas }}\n298:   selector:\n299:     matchLabels:\n300:       app: agentcube-router\n301:   template:\n302:     metadata:\n303:       labels:\n304:         app: agentcube-router\n305:     spec:\n306:       {{- with .Values.imagePullSecrets }}\n307:       imagePullSecrets:\n308:         {{- toYaml . | nindent 8 }}\n309:       {{- end }}\n310:       {{- if .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n311:       serviceAccountName: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName }}\n312:       {{- end }}\n313:       containers:\n314:         - name: agentcube-router\n315:           image: \"{{ .Values.router.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.router.image.tag }}\"\n316:           imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.router.image.pullPolicy }}\n317:           ports:\n318:             - name: http\n319:               containerPort: {{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n320:               protocol: TCP\n321:           env:\n322:             - name: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE\n323:               valueFrom:\n324:                 fieldRef:\n325:                   fieldPath: metadata.namespace\n326:             - name: REDIS_ADDR\n327:               value: {{ .Values.redis.addr | quote }}\n328:             - name: REDIS_PASSWORD\n329:               valueFrom:\n330:                 secretKeyRef:\n331:                   name: {{ .Release.Name }}-redis\n332:                   key: password\n333:                   optional: true\n334:             - name: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\n335:               value: \"http://workloadmanager.{{ .Release.Namespace }}.svc.cluster.local:{{ .Values.workloadmanager.service.port }}\"\n336:             {{- with .Values.router.extraEnv }}\n337:             {{- toYaml . | nindent 12 }}\n338:             {{- end }}\n339:           args:\n340:             - --port={{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n341:             - --debug\n342:           resources:\n343:             {{- toYaml .Values.router.resources | nindent 12 }}\n344:           livenessProbe:\n345:             httpGet:\n346:               path: /health/live\n347:               port: http\n348:             initialDelaySeconds: 1\n349:             periodSeconds: 2\n350:           readinessProbe:\n351:             httpGet:\n352:               path: /health/ready\n353:               port: http\n354:             initialDelaySeconds: 1\n355:             periodSeconds: 2\n356: ---\n357: apiVersion: v1\n358: kind: Service\n359: metadata:\n360:   name: agentcube-router\n361:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n362:   labels:\n363:     app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n364:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n365: spec:\n366:   type: {{ .Values.router.service.type }}\n367:   ports:\n368:     - port: {{ .Values.router.service.port }}\n369:       targetPort: {{ .Values.router.service.targetPort }}\n370:       protocol: TCP\n371:       name: http\n372:   selector:\n373:     app: agentcube-router\n374: ```\n375: \n376: ### 5. Workload Manager RBAC\n377: \n378: ```yaml\n379: # manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml\n380: apiVersion: v1\n381: kind: ServiceAccount\n382: metadata:\n383:   name: workloadmanager\n384:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n385:   labels:\n386:     app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n387:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n388: ---\n389: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n390: kind: ClusterRole\n391: metadata:\n392:   name: workloadmanager\n393:   labels:\n394:     app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n395:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n396: rules:\n397:   - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n398:     resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n399:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n400:   - apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n401:     resources: [\"sandboxclaims\", \"sandboxtemplates\", \"sandboxwarmpools\"]\n402:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n403:   - apiGroups: [\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n404:     resources: [\"sandboxwarmpools/status\"]\n405:     verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n406:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n407:     resources: [\"codeinterpreters\"]\n408:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n409:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n410:     resources: [\"codeinterpreters/status\"]\n411:     verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n412:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n413:     resources: [\"codeinterpreters/finalizers\"]\n414:     verbs: [\"update\"]\n415:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n416:     resources: [\"agentruntimes\"]\n417:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n418:   - apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n419:     resources: [\"agentruntimes/status\"]\n420:     verbs: [\"update\", \"patch\"]\n421:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n422:     resources: [\"pods\"]\n423:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n424:   - apiGroups: [\"authentication.k8s.io\"]\n425:     resources: [\"tokenreviews\"]\n426:     verbs: [\"create\"]\n427:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n428:     resources: [\"secrets\"]\n429:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n430: ---\n431: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n432: kind: ClusterRoleBinding\n433: metadata:\n434:   name: workloadmanager\n435:   labels:\n436:     app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager\n437:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n438: subjects:\n439:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n440:     name: workloadmanager\n441:     namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n442: roleRef:\n443:   kind: ClusterRole\n444:   name: workloadmanager\n445:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n446: ```\n447: \n448: ### 6. Router RBAC (Optional)\n449: \n450: ```yaml\n451: # manifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml\n452: {{- if .Values.router.rbac.create }}\n453: apiVersion: v1\n454: kind: ServiceAccount\n455: metadata:\n456:   name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n457:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n458:   labels:\n459:     app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n460:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n461: ---\n462: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n463: kind: Role\n464: metadata:\n465:   name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n466:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n467:   labels:\n468:     app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n469:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n470: rules:\n471:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n472:     resources: [\"secrets\"]\n473:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n474: ---\n475: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n476: kind: RoleBinding\n477: metadata:\n478:   name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n479:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n480:   labels:\n481:     app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube-router\n482:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n483: subjects:\n484:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n485:     name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n486:     namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n487: roleRef:\n488:   kind: Role\n489:   name: {{ .Values.router.serviceAccountName | default \"agentcube-router\" }}\n490:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n491: {{- end }}\n492: ```\n493: \n494: ### 7. Volcano Agent Scheduler (Optional)\n495: \n496: ```yaml\n497: # manifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\n498: {{- if .Values.volcano.scheduler.enabled }}\n499: apiVersion: v1\n500: kind: ServiceAccount\n501: metadata:\n502:   name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n503:   labels:\n504:     app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n505:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n506: ---\n507: apiVersion: v1\n508: kind: ConfigMap\n509: metadata:\n510:   name: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n511:   labels:\n512:     app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n513:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n514: data:\n515:   agent-scheduler.conf: |\n516:     actions: \"allocate\"\n517:     tiers:\n518:       - plugins: \"predicates,nodeorder\"\n519: ---\n520: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n521: kind: ClusterRole\n522: metadata:\n523:   name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n524: rules:\n525:   - apiGroups: [\"apiextensions.k8s.io\"]\n526:     resources: [\"customresourcedefinitions\"]\n527:     verbs: [\"create\", \"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]\n528:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n529:     resources: [\"events\"]\n530:     verbs: [\"create\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n531:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n532:     resources: [\"pods\"]\n533:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n534:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n535:     resources: [\"pods/status\"]\n536:     verbs: [\"update\"]\n537:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n538:     resources: [\"pods/binding\"]\n539:     verbs: [\"create\"]\n540:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n541:     resources: [\"persistentvolumeclaims\", \"persistentvolumes\"]\n542:     verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"update\"]\n543:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n544:     resources: [\"namespaces\", \"services\", \"replicationcontrollers\"]\n545:     verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"get\"]\n546:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n547:     resources: [\"resourcequotas\"]\n548:     verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\"]\n549:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n550:     resources: [\"nodes\"]\n551:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n552:   - apiGroups: [\"storage.k8s.io\"]\n553:     resources: [\"storageclasses\", \"csinodes\", \"csidrivers\", \"csistoragecapacities\", \"volumeattachments\"]\n554:     verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\"]\n555:   - apiGroups: [\"policy\"]\n556:     resources: [\"poddisruptionbudgets\"]\n557:     verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\"]\n558:   - apiGroups: [\"scheduling.k8s.io\"]\n559:     resources: [\"priorityclasses\"]\n560:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n561:   - apiGroups: [\"scheduling.incubator.k8s.io\", \"scheduling.volcano.sh\"]\n562:     resources: [\"podgroups\"]\n563:     verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"update\"]\n564:   - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n565:     resources: [\"configmaps\"]\n566:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"delete\", \"update\"]\n567:   - apiGroups: [\"apps\"]\n568:     resources: [\"daemonsets\", \"replicasets\", \"statefulsets\"]\n569:     verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"get\"]\n570:   - apiGroups: [\"coordination.k8s.io\"]\n571:     resources: [\"leases\"]\n572:     verbs: [\"get\", \"create\", \"update\", \"watch\"]\n573:   - apiGroups: [\"resource.k8s.io\"]\n574:     resources: [\"resourceclaims\", \"resourceclaims/status\"]\n575:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\"]\n576:   - apiGroups: [\"resource.k8s.io\"]\n577:     resources: [\"deviceclasses\", \"resourceslices\"]\n578:     verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\"]\n579:   - apiGroups: [\"shard.volcano.sh\"]\n580:     resources: [\"nodeshards\"]\n581:     verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"get\", \"update\"]\n582: ---\n583: apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\n584: kind: ClusterRoleBinding\n585: metadata:\n586:   name: volcano-agent-scheduler-role\n587: subjects:\n588:   - kind: ServiceAccount\n589:     name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n590:     namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n591: roleRef:\n592:   kind: ClusterRole\n593:   name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n594:   apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n595: ---\n596: apiVersion: v1\n597: kind: Service\n598: metadata:\n599:   name: volcano-agent-scheduler-service\n600:   annotations:\n601:     prometheus.io/scrape: \"true\"\n602:     prometheus.io/port: \"8080\"\n603:   labels:\n604:     app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n605:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n606: spec:\n607:   ports:\n608:     - port: 8080\n609:       targetPort: 8080\n610:       name: metrics\n611:   selector:\n612:     app: volcano-agent-scheduler\n613: ---\n614: apiVersion: apps/v1\n615: kind: Deployment\n616: metadata:\n617:   name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n618:   labels:\n619:     app.kubernetes.io/name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n620:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n621: spec:\n622:   replicas: {{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.replicas }}\n623:   selector:\n624:     matchLabels:\n625:       app: volcano-agent-scheduler\n626:   template:\n627:     metadata:\n628:       labels:\n629:         app: volcano-agent-scheduler\n630:     spec:\n631:       serviceAccountName: volcano-agent-scheduler\n632:       containers:\n633:         - name: volcano-agent-scheduler\n634:           image: \"{{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.image.tag }}\"\n635:           imagePullPolicy: {{ .Values.volcano.scheduler.image.pullPolicy }}\n636:           args:\n637:             - --scheduler-name=agent-scheduler\n638:             - --config=/config/agent-scheduler.conf\n639:           ports:\n640:             - containerPort: 8080\n641:               name: metrics\n642:           resources:\n643:             limits:\n644:               cpu: 500m\n645:               memory: 512Mi\n646:             requests:\n647:               cpu: 100m\n648:               memory: 128Mi\n649:           volumeMounts:\n650:             - name: config\n651:               mountPath: /config\n652:             - name: empty\n653:               mountPath: /tmp\n654:           securityContext:\n655:             runAsNonRoot: true\n656:             runAsUser: 1000\n657:       volumes:\n658:         - name: config\n659:           configMap:\n660:             name: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n661:         - name: empty\n662:           emptyDir: {}\n663: {{- end }}\n664: ```\n665: \n666: ### 8. Redis Secret Template\n667: \n668: ```yaml\n669: # manifests/charts/base/templates/redis-secret.yaml\n670: apiVersion: v1\n671: kind: Secret\n672: metadata:\n673:   name: {{ .Release.Name }}-redis\n674:   namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}\n675:   labels:\n676:     app.kubernetes.io/name: redis\n677:     app.kubernetes.io/instance: {{ .Release.Name }}\n678: type: Opaque\n679: stringData:\n680:   password: {{ .Values.redis.password | quote }}\n681: ```\n682: \n683: ### 9. .helmignore\n684: \n685: ```\n686: # .helmignore\n687: # Patterns to ignore when building packages.\n688: .DS_Store\n689: .git/\n690: .gitignore\n691: .bzr/\n692: .bzrignore\n693: .hg/\n694: .hgignore\n695: .svn/\n696: *.swp\n697: *.bak\n698: *.tmp\n699: *.orig\n700: *~\n701: .project\n702: .idea/\n703: *.tmproj\n704: .vscode/\n705: tests/\n706: *.md\n707: !README.md\n708: ```\n709: \n710: ### 10. 更新 CodeInterpreter CRD\n711: \n712: ```yaml\n713: # manifests/charts/base/crds/codeinterpreter.yaml\n714: # 基于 deployment/design.md 中的 codeinterpreters CRD 定义\n715: # 包含完整的 OpenAPI v3 schema\n716: ```\n717: \n718: ## Impact Analysis\n719: \n720: ### 依赖影响\n721: \n722: | 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n723: |--------|------|------|\n724: | Helm | ≥3.0 | Chart 打包和部署 |\n725: | Kubernetes | ≥1.21 | API 兼容性 |\n726: | Redis | 任意 | 外部依赖（通过 values 配置） |\n727: \n728: ### 模块依赖关系\n729: \n730: ```\n731: manifests/charts/base/\n732: ├── Chart.yaml                          # Chart 元数据\n733: ├── values.yaml                         # 默认配置\n734: ├── .helmignore                         # 打包忽略\n735: ├── crds/\n736: │   ├── agentruntime.yaml               # AgentRuntime CRD (已存在)\n737: │   └── codeinterpreter.yaml            # CodeInterpreter CRD (新增)\n738: └── templates/\n739:     ├── _helpers.tpl                    # 模板辅助函数\n740:     ├── redis-secret.yaml               # Redis Secret\n741:     ├── workloadmanager.yaml            # Workload Manager Deployment + Service\n742:     ├── agentcube-router.yaml           # Router Deployment + Service\n743:     ├── rbac/\n744:     │   └── workloadmanager.yaml        # Workload Manager RBAC\n745:     ├── rbac-router.yaml                # Router RBAC (可选)\n746:     └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  # Volcano Scheduler (可选)\n747: ```\n748: \n749: ### 向后兼容性\n750: \n751: - 首次实现，无破坏性变更风险\n752: - values.yaml 默认值遵循 spec 定义，确保向后兼容\n753: - 可选组件默认禁用（router.rbac.create=false, volcano.scheduler.enabled=false）\n754: \n755: ### 测试影响\n756: \n757: - 需要验证模板渲染的正确性（helm template）\n758: - 需要验证 values 覆盖行为\n759: - 需要验证可选组件的条件渲染\n760: - 需要验证 RBAC 权限的完整性\n761: \n762: ## Alternatives Considered\n763: \n764: ### 方案 1: 使用 Kustomize 替代 Helm\n765: \n766: **优点:**\n767: - 更轻量，无需额外工具\n768: - 原生支持 Kubernetes 声明式配置\n769: - 与 kubectl 集成更好\n770: \n771: **缺点:**\n772: - 缺少 values 配置树，参数化能力较弱\n773: - 不支持条件渲染（可选组件）\n774: - 缺少 release 管理和升级回滚机制\n775: \n776: **决策:** 选择 Helm，因为需要完整的配置管理和可选组件支持。\n777: \n778: ### 方案 2: 单一巨型模板文件\n779: \n780: **优点:**\n781: - 文件数量少，结构简单\n782: - 易于复制粘贴\n783: \n784: **缺点:**\n785: - 难以维护和调试\n786: - 无法模块化组织\n787: - 不利于团队协作\n788: \n789: **决策:** 采用模块化模板组织（每个组件独立文件），提高可维护性。\n790: \n791: ### 方案 3: 多 Chart 拆分（每个组件一个 Chart）\n792: \n793: **优点:**\n794: - 更细粒度的版本控制\n795: - 可以独立部署组件\n796: \n797: **缺点:**\n798: - 增加部署复杂度\n799: - 需要管理多个 Chart 版本\n800: - 不利于整体升级\n801: \n802: **决策:** 采用单一 Chart，因为组件间存在强耦合（如 Router 依赖 Workload Manager URL）。\n803: \n804: ### 方案 4: 使用子 Chart 管理可选组件\n805: \n806: **优点:**\n807: - 可选组件完全隔离\n808: - 可以独立版本\n809: \n810: **缺点:**\n811: - 增加 Chart 复杂度\n812: - 需要额外的依赖管理\n813: \n814: **决策:** 采用条件渲染（`{{- if .Values.xxx }}`），保持单一 Chart 结构。\n815: \n816: ## Testing Strategy\n817: \n818: ### 单元测试\n819: \n820: 1. **values.yaml 验证** - 使用 yamllint 验证 YAML 语法\n821: 2. **模板渲染测试** - `helm template` 验证生成的 YAML\n822: 3. **条件渲染测试** - 验证可选组件在不同 values 下的行为\n823: 4. **RBAC 验证** - 使用 `kubectl auth can-i` 验证权限\n824: \n825: ### 集成测试\n826: \n827: 1. **Kind 集群测试** - 在 Kind 集群上实际安装验证\n828: 2. **升级测试** - 验证 `helm upgrade` 行为\n829: 3. **回滚测试** - 验证 `helm rollback` 行为\n830: \n831: ### 测试覆盖目标\n832: \n833: - Chart.yaml: 100%（所有字段正确）\n834: - values.yaml: 100%（所有配置项有效）\n835: - 模板文件: 100%（所有组件渲染正确）\n836: - 条件分支: 100%（可选组件启用/禁用均正确）\n837: \n838: ## Acceptance Criteria\n839: \n840: - [ ] Chart.yaml 包含所有必需字段\n841: - [ ] values.yaml 包含完整的配置树\n842: - [ ] Workload Manager Deployment 和 Service 正确渲染\n843: - [ ] Router Deployment 和 Service 正确渲染\n844: - [ ] Workload Manager RBAC 权限完整\n845: - [ ] Router RBAC 条件渲染正确\n846: - [ ] Volcano Scheduler 条件渲染正确\n847: - [ ] Redis Secret 正确注入\n848: - [ ] CRD 文件完整（agentruntimes + codeinterpreters）\n849: - [ ] `helm lint` 无警告\n850: - [ ] `helm template` 生成有效 YAML\n851: - [ ] `helm install` 在 Kind 集群上成功\n852: - [ ] 组件健康检查通过\n853: \n854: ## Dependencies\n855: \n856: ### 必需依赖\n857: - Helm ≥3.0\n858: - Kubernetes ≥1.21\n859: - Redis（外部部署）\n860: \n861: ### 可选依赖\n862: - Volcano（仅当 volcano.scheduler.enabled=true）\n863: \n864: ### 被依赖\n865: - AR-017 (CRD 定义)\n866: - AR-029 (SDK 部署配置)\n867: \n868: ## Migration Notes\n869: \n870: ### 从手动部署迁移\n871: \n872: 1. 备份现有资源配置\n873: 2. 更新 values.yaml 匹配当前配置\n874: 3. 运行 `helm install` 安装新 Chart\n875: 4. 验证组件运行正常\n876: 5. 删除旧资源\n877: \n878: ### 破坏性变更\n879: 无 - 首次实现。\n880: \n881: ### 行为变更\n882: - Redis 配置从环境变量改为通过 Secret 注入\n883: - RBAC 资源名称标准化为组件名\n884: \n885: ## Open Questions\n886: \n887: 1. 是否支持多集群部署？（未来通过 values 覆盖实现）\n888: 2. 是否需要支持外部 Redis Operator？（待需求明确）\n889: 3. 是否需要集成监控和日志配置？（作为未来增强）\n890: \n891: ## References\n892: \n893: - `deployment/spec.md` - 部署规范\n894: - `deployment/design.md` - 部署设计\n895: - `manifests/charts/base/crds/agentruntime.yaml` - 现有 CRD\n896: - Helm Best Practices: https://helm.sh/docs/chart_best_practices/\n\n(End of file - total 896 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Helm Chart 模板与 Values 配置，提供标准的 Kubernetes 部署能力。该 Helm Chart 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件的核心部署载体，支撑 Workload Manager、Router、以及可选的 Volcano Agent Scheduler 的安装与管理。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **标准化部署流程** - 通过 Helm Chart 统一控制平面组件的部署配置，支持一键安装/升级\n2. **配置灵活性** - 通过 values.yaml 提供完整的配置项，支持镜像、资源、副本数等自定义\n3. **CRD 生命周期管理** - 将 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 纳入 Chart 管理，随 Chart 安装\n4. **Redis 连接配置** - 支持 Redis 地址和认证的灵活配置，满足 Workload Manager 和 Router 运行时需求\n5. **可选组件支持** - 支持 Router RBAC、Volcano Scheduler 等可选组件的按需启用\n6. **多环境兼容** - 通过 values 覆盖支持开发、测试、生产环境的差异化配置\n\n本实现基于 deployment/spec.md 和 deployment/design.md 的规范，遵循 Helm 3 最佳实践。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** manifests  ","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775881169242,"end":1775881169270}}}}
