{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881294160,"sessionID":"ses_2853c090cffeel1fslks36nfqD","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac495b60017LeI23NTqeX5ta","messageID":"msg_d7ac489f30015i7jLfp08SupUk","sessionID":"ses_2853c090cffeel1fslks36nfqD","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_832fa79d3c664d69b6441570","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md","content":"# AR-032: Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images)\n\n## Purpose\n\n本提案实现 AgentCube 项目的 Dockerfile 多阶段构建，为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 三个核心组件提供独立的容器镜像构建能力。该 Dockerfile 是 AgentCube 控制平面组件容器化的基础，支撑 Helm Chart 部署和 Kubernetes 运行时环境。\n\n目标是：\n\n1. **多阶段构建优化** - 使用多阶段构建减少最终镜像体积，仅包含运行必需的二进制文件和配置\n2. **三镜像分离** - 为 Workload Manager、Router、Volcano Agent Scheduler 分别构建独立镜像，支持差异化部署\n3. **最小化攻击面** - 基于 distroless 或 alpine 基础镜像，减少安全漏洞风险\n4. **构建可复用** - 统一的 Dockerfile 模板支持本地构建、CI/CD 流水线、多架构支持\n5. **环境一致性** - 确保开发、测试、生产环境的镜像构建行为一致\n6. **版本可追溯** - 镜像标签与 Git commit/Tag 关联，支持版本追踪和回滚\n\n本提案基于 deployment/design.md 和 deployment/spec.md 的规范，遵循 Docker 多阶段构建最佳实践。\n\n## Scope\n\n**Module:** docker  \n**Language:** Dockerfile  \n**Size:** S\n\n本 AR 包含：\n\n- **包含内容：**\n  - Dockerfile.workloadmanager - Workload Manager 镜像构建\n  - Dockerfile.router - Router 镜像构建\n  - Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler - Volcano Agent Scheduler 镜像构建\n  - .dockerignore 文件 - 构建上下文忽略规则\n  - Makefile 构建目标 - 简化镜像构建命令\n  - 镜像验证脚本 - 验证镜像大小、层数、安全性\n  - 构建文档和使用示例\n\n- **不包含内容：**\n  - Helm Chart 模板（由 AR-030 管理）\n  - Kubernetes 部署配置\n  - CI/CD 流水线配置\n  - 镜像仓库推送逻辑\n\n## Current State Analysis\n\n### 现有构建状态\n\n根据项目结构 `cmd/` 目录：\n- `cmd/agentcube/` - Workload Manager 源码（Go）\n- `cmd/agentcube-admin/` - 管理工具（Go）\n- `cmd/agentcube-proxy/` - 代理服务（Go）\n- `cmd/agentcube-shell/` - Shell 工具（Go）\n- `cmd/agentd/` - Agent Daemon（Go，已有二进制文件）\n- `cmd/cli/` - CLI 工具（Python）\n\n当前无 Dockerfile，缺少容器化构建能力。\n\n### 参考设计规范\n\n根据 `deployment/design.md` 和 `deployment/spec.md`：\n\n**镜像要求：**\n- Workload Manager: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口\n- Router: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口\n- Volcano Agent Scheduler: 基于 Go 二进制文件，暴露 8080 端口（metrics）\n\n**基础镜像要求：**\n- 生产镜像：使用 gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11 或 alpine:3.18\n- 构建镜像：使用 golang:1.21-bookworm\n\n**镜像标签规范：**\n- latest - 最新开发版本\n- <version> - 语义化版本（如 0.1.0）\n- <commit-sha> - Git commit SHA\n\n### 差距分析\n\n1. **缺少 Dockerfile** - 无任何 Dockerfile，无法构建容器镜像\n2. **缺少构建优化** - 未使用多阶段构建，镜像体积可能过大\n3. **缺少安全加固** - 未使用 distroless 或最小化基础镜像\n4. **缺少构建自动化** - 无 Makefile 构建目标或脚本\n\n### deployment/spec.md 关键要求\n\n1. **镜像分离** - 每个组件独立镜像，避免耦合\n2. **端口暴露** - Workload Manager 8080, Router 8080, Scheduler 8080 (metrics)\n3. **环境变量** - 支持 REDIS_ADDR, REDIS_PASSWORD, AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE 等\n4. **健康检查** - Docker HEALTHCHECK 指令配置\n5. **非 root 用户** - 生产镜像以非 root 用户运行\n\n## Proposed Changes\n\n### 1. 目录结构\n\n```\ndocker/\n├── .dockerignore                       # 构建上下文忽略\n├── Dockerfile.workloadmanager          # Workload Manager Dockerfile\n├── Dockerfile.router                   # Router Dockerfile\n├── Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler  # Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile\n├── Makefile                            # 构建目标\n├── validate.sh                         # 镜像验证脚本\n└── README.md                           # 构建说明文档\n```\n\n### 2. .dockerignore\n\n```dockerignore\n# .dockerignore\n# Build context ignores\n\n# Git\n.git\n.gitignore\n\n# Build artifacts\nbin/\ndist/\n*.out\n\n# Dependencies\nvendor/\n\n# IDE\n.idea/\n.vscode/\n*.swp\n*.swo\n\n# Documentation\n*.md\n!README.md\n\n# Tests\ntesting/\n*_test.go\n\n# Docker\ndocker/\nDockerfile*\n\n# Helm\nmanifests/\n\n# Python\n__pycache__/\n*.pyc\n.pytest_cache/\n\n# Misc\n.DS_Store\nThumbs.db\n```\n\n### 3. Workload Manager Dockerfile\n\n```dockerfile\n# docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager\n# Multi-stage build for Workload Manager\n\n# Stage 1: Build\nFROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n\nWORKDIR /build\n\n# Copy go mod files\nCOPY go.mod go.sum ./\nRUN go mod download\n\n# Copy source code\nCOPY cmd/agentcube ./cmd/agentcube\nCOPY pkg ./pkg\n\n# Build the binary\nRUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n    -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n    -o /build/workloadmanager \\\n    ./cmd/agentcube\n\n# Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\nFROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n\n# Copy binary from builder\nCOPY --from=builder /build/workloadmanager /workloadmanager\n\n# Set non-root user\nUSER nonroot:nonroot\n\n# Set working directory\nWORKDIR /\n\n# Expose port\nEXPOSE 8080\n\n# Health check\nHEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n    CMD [\"/workloadmanager\", \"--health\"]\n\n# Entrypoint\nENTRYPOINT [\"/workloadmanager\"]\nCMD [\"--port=8080\"]\n```\n\n### 4. Router Dockerfile\n\n```dockerfile\n# docker/Dockerfile.router\n# Multi-stage build for Router\n\n# Stage 1: Build\nFROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n\nWORKDIR /build\n\n# Copy go mod files\nCOPY go.mod go.sum ./\nRUN go mod download\n\n# Copy source code\nCOPY cmd/agentcube-proxy ./cmd/agentcube-proxy\nCOPY pkg ./pkg\n\n# Build the binary\nRUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n    -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n    -o /build/router \\\n    ./cmd/agentcube-proxy\n\n# Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\nFROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n\n# Copy binary from builder\nCOPY --from=builder /build/router /router\n\n# Set non-root user\nUSER nonroot:nonroot\n\n# Set working directory\nWORKDIR /\n\n# Expose port\nEXPOSE 8080\n\n# Health check\nHEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n    CMD [\"/router\", \"--health\"]\n\n# Entrypoint\nENTRYPOINT [\"/router\"]\nCMD [\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]\n```\n\n### 5. Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile\n\n```dockerfile\n# docker/Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler\n# Multi-stage build for Volcano Agent Scheduler\n\n# Stage 1: Build\nFROM golang:1.21-bookworm AS builder\n\nWORKDIR /build\n\n# Copy go mod files\nCOPY go.mod go.sum ./\nRUN go mod download\n\n# Copy source code\nCOPY cmd/agentd ./cmd/agentd\nCOPY pkg ./pkg\n\n# Build the binary\nRUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build \\\n    -ldflags=\"-w -s\" \\\n    -o /build/volcano-agent-scheduler \\\n    ./cmd/agentd\n\n# Stage 2: Runtime (distroless)\nFROM gcr.io/distroless/static-debian11:nonroot AS runtime\n\n# Copy binary from builder\nCOPY --from=builder /build/volcano-agent-scheduler /volcano-agent-scheduler\n\n# Copy default config\nCOPY sandbox-orchestration/agent-scheduler.conf /config/agent-scheduler.conf\n\n# Set non-root user\nUSER nonroot:nonroot\n\n# Set working directory\nWORKDIR /\n\n# Expose metrics port\nEXPOSE 8080\n\n# Health check\nHEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n    CMD [\"/volcano-agent-scheduler\", \"--health\"]\n\n# Entrypoint\nENTRYPOINT [\"/volcano-agent-scheduler\"]\nCMD [\"--scheduler-name=agent-scheduler\", \"--config=/config/agent-scheduler.conf\"]\n```\n\n### 6. Makefile Build Targets\n\n```makefile\n# Makefile (add to root or docker/Makefile)\n\n# Docker build configuration\nDOCKER_REGISTRY ?= ghcr.io/volcano-sh\nDOCKER_TAG ?= latest\nVERSION ?= $(shell git describe --tags --always --dirty)\nCOMMIT_SHA ?= $(shell git rev-parse --short HEAD)\n\n# Image names\nWORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/workloadmanager\nROUTER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/agentcube-router\nVOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE := $(DOCKER_REGISTRY)/vc-agent-scheduler\n\n# Build targets\n.PHONY: docker-build\ndocker-build: docker-build-workloadmanager docker-build-router docker-build-scheduler\n\n.PHONY: docker-build-workloadmanager\ndocker-build-workloadmanager:\n\tdocker build \\\n\t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager \\\n\t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n\t\t-t $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n\t\t.\n\n.PHONY: docker-build-router\ndocker-build-router:\n\tdocker build \\\n\t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.router \\\n\t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n\t\t-t $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n\t\t.\n\n.PHONY: docker-build-scheduler\ndocker-build-scheduler:\n\tdocker build \\\n\t\t-f docker/Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler \\\n\t\t-t $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) \\\n\t\t-t $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA) \\\n\t\t.\n\n.PHONY: docker-push\ndocker-push: docker-push-workloadmanager docker-push-router docker-push-scheduler\n\n.PHONY: docker-push-workloadmanager\ndocker-push-workloadmanager:\n\tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n\tdocker push $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n\n.PHONY: docker-push-router\ndocker-push-router:\n\tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n\tdocker push $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n\n.PHONY: docker-push-scheduler\ndocker-push-scheduler:\n\tdocker push $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG)\n\tdocker push $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(COMMIT_SHA)\n\n.PHONY: docker-validate\ndocker-validate:\n\t./docker/validate.sh\n\n.PHONY: docker-clean\ndocker-clean:\n\tdocker rmi $(WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n\tdocker rmi $(ROUTER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n\tdocker rmi $(VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE):$(DOCKER_TAG) 2>/dev/null || true\n```\n\n### 7. 镜像验证脚本\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# docker/validate.sh\n\nset -e\n\nWORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/workloadmanager:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\nROUTER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/agentcube-router:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\nVOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE=\"${DOCKER_REGISTRY:-ghcr.io/volcano-sh}/vc-agent-scheduler:${DOCKER_TAG:-latest}\"\n\necho \"Validating Docker images...\"\necho \"\"\n\n# Function to check image\ncheck_image() {\n    local image=$1\n    local name=$2\n    \n    echo \"Checking $name...\"\n    \n    # Check if image exists\n    if ! docker image inspect \"$image\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n        echo \"  ✗ Image not found: $image\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n    echo \"  ✓ Image exists\"\n    \n    # Check image size (should be < 50MB for distroless)\n    local size=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{.Size}}')\n    local size_mb=$((size / 1024 / 1024))\n    if [ $size_mb -lt 50 ]; then\n        echo \"  ✓ Image size: ${size_mb}MB (< 50MB)\"\n    else\n        echo \"  ✗ Image size: ${size_mb}MB (>= 50MB)\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n    \n    # Check layer count (should be <= 5)\n    local layers=$(docker image history \"$image\" --format='{{.ID}}' | wc -l)\n    if [ $layers -le 5 ]; then\n        echo \"  ✓ Layer count: $layers (<= 5)\"\n    else\n        echo \"  ✗ Layer count: $layers (> 5)\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n    \n    # Check if running as non-root\n    local user=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{.Config.User}}')\n    if [ -n \"$user\" ] && [ \"$user\" != \"root\" ]; then\n        echo \"  ✓ Running as non-root: $user\"\n    else\n        echo \"  ✗ Running as root or no user specified\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n    \n    # Check exposed ports\n    local ports=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{json .Config.ExposedPorts}}')\n    if echo \"$ports\" | grep -q \"8080\"; then\n        echo \"  ✓ Port 8080 exposed\"\n    else\n        echo \"  ✗ Port 8080 not exposed\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n    \n    # Check health check\n    local healthcheck=$(docker image inspect \"$image\" --format='{{json .Config.Healthcheck}}')\n    if [ \"$healthcheck\" != \"null\" ] && [ -n \"$healthcheck\" ]; then\n        echo \"  ✓ Health check configured\"\n    else\n        echo \"  ✗ Health check not configured\"\n        return 1\n    fi\n    \n    echo \"\"\n}\n\n# Validate all images\ncheck_image \"$WORKLOADMANAGER_IMAGE\" \"Workload Manager\"\ncheck_image \"$ROUTER_IMAGE\" \"Router\"\ncheck_image \"$VOLCANO_SCHEDULER_IMAGE\" \"Volcano Agent Scheduler\"\n\necho \"All validations passed!\"\n```\n\n### 8. 构建文档 (docker/README.md)\n\n```markdown\n# Docker Image Builds\n\nAgentCube 控制平面组件的 Docker 镜像构建配置。\n\n## 镜像列表\n\n| 组件 | 镜像名 | 端口 | 大小目标 |\n|------|--------|------|----------|\n| Workload Manager | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager | 8080 | < 50MB |\n| Router | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router | 8080 | < 50MB |\n| Volcano Agent Scheduler | ghcr.io/volcano-sh/vc-agent-scheduler | 8080 | < 50MB |\n\n## 快速开始\n\n### 构建所有镜像\n\n```bash\nmake docker-build\n```\n\n### 构建单个镜像\n\n```bash\nmake docker-build-workloadmanager\nmake docker-build-router\nmake docker-build-scheduler\n```\n\n### 推送镜像\n\n```bash\nmake docker-push\n```\n\n### 验证镜像\n\n```bash\nmake docker-validate\n```\n\n## 自定义配置\n\n### 修改镜像仓库\n\n```bash\nexport DOCKER_REGISTRY=myregistry.com\nmake docker-build\n```\n\n### 修改镜像标签\n\n```bash\nexport DOCKER_TAG=v0.1.0\nmake docker-build\n```\n\n## 多架构支持\n\n```bash\ndocker buildx build \\\n  --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \\\n  -t ghcr.io/volcano-sh/workloadmanager:latest \\\n  --push \\\n  -f docker/Dockerfile.workloadmanager \\\n  .\n```\n\n## 安全最佳实践\n\n1. **非 root 用户** - 所有镜像以 nonroot 用户运行\n2. **Distroless 基础** - 使用 distroless/static-debian11 减少攻击面\n3. **多阶段构建** - 仅复制必需的二进制文件\n4. **静态链接** - CGO_ENABLED=0 避免动态库依赖\n5. **健康检查** - 配置 HEALTHCHECK 指令\n\n## 故障排查\n\n### 镜像构建失败\n\n检查 Go 代码是否能编译：\n```bash\ngo build -o /tmp/test ./cmd/agentcube\n```\n\n### 镜像过大\n\n检查是否包含了不必要的文件：\n```bash\ndocker history <image-name>\n```\n\n### 权限错误\n\n确保 Docker daemon 正常运行：\n```bash\ndocker info\n```\n```\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### 依赖影响\n\n| 依赖项 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| Docker | ≥20.10 | 镜像构建 |\n| Go | ≥1.21 | 应用编译 |\n| Make | 任意 | 构建自动化 |\n\n### 模块依赖关系\n\n```\ndocker/\n├── .dockerignore                       # 无依赖\n├── Dockerfile.workloadmanager          # 依赖 cmd/agentcube, pkg/\n├── Dockerfile.router                   # 依赖 cmd/agentcube-proxy, pkg/\n├── Dockerfile.volcano-agent-scheduler  # 依赖 cmd/agentd, pkg/\n├── Makefile                            # 依赖所有 Dockerfile\n├── validate.sh                         # 依赖 docker CLI\n└── README.md                           # 文档\n```\n\n### 向后兼容性\n\n- 首次实现，无破坏性变更风险\n- 镜像标签策略支持版本追溯\n- 多架构支持未来扩展\n\n### 测试影响\n\n- 需要验证镜像构建成功\n- 需要验证镜像大小符合目标\n- 需要验证容器可正常启动\n- 需要验证健康检查有效\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### 方案 1: 单 Dockerfile 多目标构建\n\n**优点:**\n- 单一文件，易于维护\n- 使用 BUILDKIT 多目标\n\n**缺点:**\n- 文件过大，难以阅读\n- 不便于独立构建\n\n**决策:** 采用独立 Dockerfile，每个组件一个文件。\n\n### 方案 2: 使用 Alpine 基础镜像\n\n**优点:**\n- 镜像体积小\n- 包管理方便\n\n**缺点:**\n- 存在已知安全漏洞\n- glibc 兼容性问题\n\n**决策:** 采用 distroless/static-debian11，更安全。\n\n### 方案 3: 单一巨型镜像（包含所有组件）\n\n**优点:**\n- 单一镜像，部署简单\n- 减少镜像数量\n\n**缺点:**\n- 镜像体积大\n- 安全风险高\n- 无法独立部署组件\n\n**决策:** 采用独立镜像，支持最小化部署。\n\n### 方案 4: 使用 Buildpacks\n\n**优点:**\n- 自动化程度高\n- 无需 Dockerfile\n\n**缺点:**\n- 定制化能力弱\n- 无法精确控制镜像内容\n\n**决策:** 采用 Dockerfile，保持完全控制。\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### 构建测试\n\n1. **本地构建测试** - 验证所有 Dockerfile 可成功构建\n2. **镜像大小测试** - 验证镜像体积 < 50MB\n3. **层数测试** - 验证镜像层数 <= 5\n\n### 功能测试\n\n1. **容器启动测试** - 验证容器可正常启动\n2. **健康检查测试** - 验证 HEALTHCHECK 有效\n3. **端口暴露测试** - 验证 8080 端口可访问\n\n### 安全测试\n\n1. **非 root 测试** - 验证容器以非 root 用户运行\n2. **漏洞扫描** - 使用 Trivy 扫描镜像漏洞\n3. **最小权限测试** - 验证容器无多余权限\n\n### 测试覆盖目标\n\n- Dockerfile: 100%（所有指令正确）\n- 构建脚本：100%（所有目标有效）\n- 验证脚本：100%（所有检查项通过）\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Workload Manager Dockerfile 可成功构建\n- [ ] Router Dockerfile 可成功构建\n- [ ] Volcano Agent Scheduler Dockerfile 可成功构建\n- [ ] 镜像大小 < 50MB\n- [ ] 镜像层数 <= 5\n- [ ] 容器以非 root 用户运行\n- [ ] 健康检查配置正确\n- [ ] 端口 8080 暴露\n- [ ] Makefile 构建目标可用\n- [ ] 验证脚本通过所有检查\n- [ ] 文档完整（构建说明、故障排查）\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### 必需依赖\n- Docker ≥20.10\n- Go ≥1.21\n- Make\n\n### 可选依赖\n- Docker Buildx（多架构支持）\n- Trivy（安全扫描）\n\n### 被依赖\n- AR-030 (Helm Chart) - 镜像用于 Helm Chart 部署\n- cmd/agentcube, cmd/agentcube-proxy, cmd/agentd - 应用源码\n\n## Migration Notes\n\n### 从手动构建迁移\n\n1. 安装 Docker 和 Go 1.21+\n2. 运行 `make docker-build` 构建镜像\n3. 验证镜像 `make docker-validate`\n4. 更新 Helm values.yaml 使用新镜像\n\n### 破坏性变更\n无 - 首次实现。\n\n### 行为变更\n- 从源码编译改为容器化部署\n- 从直接运行改为容器运行\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. 是否需要支持 Windows 容器？（未来扩展）\n2. 是否需要集成镜像签名？（待需求明确）\n3. 是否需要支持自定义基础镜像？（待需求明确）\n\n## References\n\n- `deployment/spec.md` - 部署规范\n- `deployment/design.md` - 部署设计\n- `cmd/agentcube/` - Workload Manager 源码\n- `cmd/agentcube-proxy/` - Router 源码\n- `cmd/agentd/` - Volcano Agent Scheduler 源码\n- Docker Best Practices: https://docs.docker.com/develop/develop-images/dockerfile_best-practices/\n- Distroless Images: https://github.com/GoogleContainerTools/distroless\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-032/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775881294142,"end":1775881294155}}}}
